{"tid":694782,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"華星真係咁好食？","createTime":"2018-06-08T15:31:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-08T17:06:33.000Z","uid":74629,"like":10,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c404140a0c8c1c8d86674ea9d25c17250b09df60","tid":694782,"uid":74629,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:31:45.000Z","msg":"今日lunch time行過見好多人食<br />\n見未試過就入去試下<br />\n<br />\n佢個menu好似唔多選擇<br />\n想飽肚就淨係得常餐<br />\n個常餐有啲似普通茶餐廳嘅早餐咁<br />\n但都已經要$4x<br />\n<br />\n點解呢間野會有咁多人食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"484e6e89b9526bc3cb29a159ff8693e6fa201c3e","tid":694782,"uid":12633,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:35:54.000Z","msg":"唔可以話難食，但唔算好食"},{"pid":"8866e77ad624b4ec6e1a34b219ed074b4bec38fe","tid":694782,"uid":86673,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:36:35.000Z","msg":"唔抵食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c3dcae4fd786b37ff6f5266218e5a55b66f3545","tid":694782,"uid":74629,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T15:41:10.000Z","msg":"唔係難食<br />\n但又未至於好食到有咁多人排隊<br />\n<br />\n咁啱今日做野途經旺角，見到有人排隊裏面又full哂<br />\n以為應該有啲水準<br />\n但除左個炒蛋覺得幾好食之外，其他都係普普通通<br />\n張枱又窄到西咁<br />\n食都食得唔舒服"},{"pid":"a0dd05e7c75991e6a137b9f848ed25e960674a58","tid":694782,"uid":127466,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:35:31.000Z","msg":"灣仔果間試過一次,無下次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  D位窄到, 迫到埋水 bar 枱到, 個頭差不多頂到張水 bar 枱. d 野食唔好食, 北海渡差極都好過佢, 又可以去瑞士茶記食..等鬼死咁耐仲要出埋d普通茶記料. 除左慣性鍾意同人迫既, 唸唔到點解仲會有咁多人幫襯 !"},{"pid":"fac173cf6c6b8042aa6370306395c07dc2cfdb74","tid":694782,"uid":49941,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:51:05.000Z","msg":"淨計出名啲嘅冰室 華星可以叫正正常常<br />\n文華集團式經營唔洗講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n澳牛比錢買難受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n華嫂直頭係唔好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"450d4d2c39107536504ce5766906758f5f1856e3","tid":694782,"uid":5006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:54:02.000Z","msg":"元朗果間無人食咁濟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n今日去食 幾撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最鐘意佢少野簡 但啲料已經夠做<br />\n但價錢真心貴 食碟粉接近50蚊 所以睇你點睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b2423f44956fbaf5ab7d7bbd60174bb1dc7b2054","tid":694782,"uid":3535,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:06:33.000Z","msg":"冇特別"}]}